en_134617_0	A motor vehicle has been ablazed near Borella Cemetery this evening.
en_134617_1	The vehicle has been completely burned down and the Colombo District Fire-Fighters have come to the scene and doused the fire, Borella Police states.
en_134617_2	The driver has jumped out of the vehicle and saved himself.
en_134617_3	The fire has taken place due to a technical short-circuit.
